Package org.goplanit.utils.zoning

Interface Centroid

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IdAble>, IdAble, ManagedId, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CentroidImpl
    public interface Centroid
extends ManagedId, Serializable
    A centroid is a singular spatial location in a zone that is deemed most representative if the zone's geometry were to be condensed into a single point
    Author:
    markr
